    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors scoped out per MRL 2 requirements with documented justification. Validation results demonstrate NIH predictions within experimental uncertainty across all 5 operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Assessment accepted.",
